## What This Does

The AI Workflow Auditor takes a description of a business's day-to-day workflows and uses Claude AI to produce a structured, prioritised report of automation opportunities — ranked by impact and effort.

Built to demonstrate practical AI integration: a frontend form, an n8n automation layer, the Claude API, and an Airtable database — all connected and working together.

