## How It Works

1. User fills in a form describing their business and up to 5 workflows
2. Form submission triggers an n8n webhook
3. n8n sends the data to the Claude API with a structured prompt
4. Claude returns a JSON report of automation opportunities
5. n8n formats the report and returns it to the user as a readable HTML page
6. The audit is logged to Airtable for tracking

---

## Architecture
```
[Web Form]
    ↓ HTTP POST
[n8n Webhook]
    ↓
[Claude API]
    ↓ JSON
[n8n — Parse + Format]
    ↓                    ↓
[HTML Report]       [Airtable Log]
```

