## Running This Locally

### Prerequisites
- n8n account (cloud or self-hosted)
- Anthropic API key — [get one here](https://console.anthropic.com)
- Airtable account and API key

### Setup

1. Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Negbepierre/ai-workflow-auditor.git
cd ai-workflow-auditor
```

2. Copy the environment variables file
```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

3. Add your API keys to `.env`
```
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key_here
AIRTABLE_API_KEY=your_key_here
AIRTABLE_BASE_ID=your_base_id_here
```

4. Import the n8n workflow (instructions in [MANUAL.md](docs/MANUAL.md))

5. Open `form/index.html` in your browser and run your first audit

